snippet.description:

#WashiYoWashi in the thunderous voice of Pawan Kalyan üí•

#OG #TheyCallHimOG

NAKODA & Japanese drums - Sivamani

Cast - Pawan Kalyan, Emraan Hashmi, Priyanka Arul Mohan, Arjun Das, Sriya Reddy, Prakash Raj

Movie Name: They Call Him OG
Written & Directed by Sujeeth
Music by Thaman S
Production: DVV Entertainment
Presented by: Smt D.Parvathi
Produced by DVV Danayya, Kalyan Dasari
Cinematographers : Ravi K Chandran (ISC), Manoj Paramahamsa (ISC)
Production Designer : AS Prakash
Editor: Navin Nooli
Costume Designers: Darshan Jalan & Neelanchal Kumar Ghosh
Creative Director : Ashwin Mani
Creative Producer : Harish Pai
Action Masters : A Vijay, Peter Hein, Dhilip Subbarayan, Kevin Kumar, Stunt Silva, Sunil Rodrigues, Kecha Khampakdee, Juji, Supreme Sundar, Jashwa, Parvez
Co-director: Somaraju PVV
Direction Department : Uday Alla, Aarun Thevar, Lokesh Srinivasan, Kishore Sarella,
Kedar Pashikanti, Durga D.R, Sainadh Alla, Mithilesh Sivagani, Rithica Devireddy,
I.Chaitanya Sravanth, N.Sruti Ranjani, RSN.Roshan Sharif
Chief Associate Editors : Raam tumu, Srinu Bainaboyina
Associate Editors: Prashanth Tej, Yogi (D.F.Tech), Vishnu ramagiri
Executive Producer: Sathyanarayana Guggilla
Production Controller: Manikanta Rongala
Sound Design : Sync Cinema
VFX Supervisor : Raghav Tammareddy
Stills : Mallesh Thatha
Marketing: Walls and Trends
PRO: Venugopal
DI : Annapurna Studios
Marketing : Walls & Trends
Video composition: Walls & Trends
Lyrics -
WASHI YO WASHI 
EAGLE OH EAGLE 

Yasei no washi o korosu ni wa 
To kill a wild Eagle 

Mazu tsubasa o kiri otosu hitsu yoo ga aru 
You need to cut its wings first 

Jimen ni ochitara..me o eguri dasu 
When it falls on the ground you pluck its eyes 

Me ga mienaku nari, doko ni ikeba ii no ka wakara naku suru 
It becomes blind and doesn‚Äôt know where to go 

Sokode ashi o kitte ugokenaku suru 
That‚Äôs when you cut its legs and make it immobile 

Soshite, yasei no shinzou o eguri dasu noda 
And that‚Äôs when you will pluck its wild heart out 

WASHI YO WASHI 
EAGLE O EAGLE

snippet.description:
KRAMP Teaser on Hasya Movies.

KRAMP is an Upcoming 2025 Telugu Movie Starring Kiran Abbavaraam, Yukti Thareja & Others. Directed by Jains Nani. Music by Chaitan Bharadwaj. snippet.title: Nallaru Po | Dude | Pradeep Ranganathan | @SaiAbhyankkar | Tippu | Mohit Chauhan | Keerthiswaran
snippet.description:
Presenting the Lyrical Video song of 'Nallaru po' from 'Dude', Written & Directed by Keerthiswaran featuring Pradeep Ranganathan, Mamitha Baiju, R.Sarath Kumar, Hridhu Haroon,Rohini, Aishwarya sharma, Dravid selvam & Others.

An @SaiAbhyankkar  Musical 
Song Title: 'Nallaru po'
Album: Dude

Music Credits:

Composed and produced by @SaiAbhyankkar 
Singers: Tipu , @SaiAbhyankkar  & Mohit Chauhan
Lyricist : Vivek 
Synth ,keys and Bass programmed by @SaiAbhyankkar 
Acoustic ,Electric Bass Guitar & Charango - Keba

Lyrics:

Nee ketaa unna kooda un kaiyil vittu poguren
Aasa pola vaazhndhukkoyen po
Un mela kaadhal vachene
Thothadhaalum theerala
Ponadhaalum maarala 

Nee ketaa unna kooda un kaiyil vittu poguren
Aasa pola vaazhndhukko di po
Ennalum Kaadhal kuthadhu 
Parvayal Yenga Vechaale 

Paakaama pesaama seraama ponaalum 
Ennaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum
Neeyaachum nallaaru po
 
Kaadhalaa en nenjam
Yekkamaa aanan naane
Kaayamaa nee senjum
Sirikkirene
Yaaradi kutham solla 
En vidhi  enna kolla 
Nee vantha nenjukkulla  
Ippothu onnumilla 

Veroru kayyoda un veral paathen naane 
Vegura nenjoda pogurene
Nethu un kannil naane
Innaikku yaaro dhaane 
Thindaadurene maane
Thaa po nu vittutene 

Paakaama pesaama enkuda seraama ponaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum 
Neeyaachum nallaarupo 

Hey Innoruthanoda nee poga 
Ullolachaloda naan poga 
Enna panna poren Thikku theriyaadhe 
Aanaa neeyum po
 
Hey Ennapanna poren kekaadha
Indha pakkam neeyum paakaadha
Michamulla kaadhal atchadhaya podum 
Nallaa vaazhu po

Yaaradi kutham solla 
En vidhi  enna kolla 
Nee vantha nenjukkulla  
Ippothu onnumilla 

Veroru kayyoda un veral paathen naane 
Vegura nenjoda pogurene
Nethu un kannil naane
Innaikku yaaro dhaane 
Thindaadurene maane
Thaa po nu vittutene 

Paakaama pesaama enkuda seraama ponaalum nallaru po 
Hey thaangaama thoongaama naan inga vaazhndhaalum 
Neeyaachum nallaarupo 

Hey Innoruthanoda nee poga 
Ullolachaloda naan poga 
Enna panna poren Thikku theriyaadhe 
Aanaa neeyum po
 
Hey Ennapanna poren kekaadha
Indha pakkam neeyum paakaadha
Michamulla kaadhal atchadhaya podum 
Nallaa vaazhu po

Thanks for Watching ‚ù£Ô∏è

Vrusshabha is an upcoming Indian epic action-drama film written and directed by Nanda Kishore. It stars Mohanlal in the lead role, alongside Roshan Meka, Shanaya Kapoor, Zahrah S. Khan, Srikanth Meka, and Ragini Dwivedi.The film is simultaneously shot in Telugu and Malayalam and will be released in five languages. It is the land where people stand together in every storm, ready to live, love, and even die for each other. Punjab is fire, Punjab is faith, Punjab is love ‚Äî a place where passion runs deeper than rivers, and where humanity knows no religion. Punjab is not just a name, it is an eternal emotion that will live forever in the hearts of those who belong to it.‚Äù

snippet.title: Vikram Sarkar - Naam Chale (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
Vikram Sarkar - Naam Chale
Stream/Download ~

~ MUSIC INFO ~ 
Song - Naam Chale
Artist - Vikram Sarkar
Lyricis - Vikram Sarkar
Musician - Thought Music

~ Lyrics ~ Vikram Sarkar - Naam Chale
Ghumti game chle 
Goj me fame chle 
Note jit na chale 
Yaar ka name chle bby 
Gail me mam chle 
Top ka time chle 
Note jit naa chaale 
Yaar ka time chale bby 

Dunia me horya shor dekh 
Tu krke chori gor dekh 
Meri k dekhe tu ankhyan me 
Tu bas vikram Ki taur dekh 
Na ger pyar k fande ne 
Na puch tu chori dhnde ne 
M gailyan rakhu 4 mistri 
Khol k dhr de bande ne 
Virodhi sehm chle 
Kadhta bhem chle 
Note jit na chaale 
Yaar ka name chle bby 

Khulle se khate na pdte hisaban me 
Masti me rehte hum rehte na yadan me 
1 life mili bby jee re swadan me 
Talented balak na pdte vivaadan me 
Tu dekh yaar auda 
Se ped na samjhe paudha 
Mne kehke system paade se 
Firr tu bby k sauda 
Bairi ne rakhu koda 
Dharti lgwadu goda 
Chal manya thoda ghaat krya 
Par kaam krya naa boda bby 
Vibe na same chle 
Mind me aim chle 
Note jit naa chaale 
Yaar ka name chale bby
